  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "First listen and then answer the question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "先听录音，然后回答问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "What evidence is there of a ghost?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "有什么证据表明那里有鬼？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "A public house which was recently bought by Mr.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "汤普森先生最近买下的一家"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "Thompson is up for sale.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "酒馆正在出售。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "Mr.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "汤普森先生"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "Thompson is going to sell it because it is haunted.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "准备卖掉它，因为那里闹鬼。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "He told me that he could not go to sleep one night because he heard a strange noise coming from the bar.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他告诉我，有天夜里他无法入睡，因为听到酒吧间里传来一种奇怪的声音。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "The next morning he found that the doors had been blocked by chairs and the furniture had been moved.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第二天早晨，他发现门被椅子堵住了，家具也被移动过。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "Though Mr.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "虽然汤普森先生"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "Thompson had turned the lights off before he went to bed, they were on in the morning.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "睡前关了灯，但早晨灯却亮着。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "He also said that he had found five empty whiskey bottles which the ghost must have drunk the night before.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他还说自己发现了五只空威士忌酒瓶，想必是鬼前一晚喝空的。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "When I suggested that some villagers must have come in for a free drink, Mr.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我提出也许是几个村民进来白喝了一顿时，汤普森先生"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "Thompson shook his head.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "摇了摇头。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "text": "The villagers have told him that they will not accept the pub even if he gives it away.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "村民们告诉他，即使他把酒馆白送给他们，他们也不会要。"
      }
    }
  ],
